  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd  \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The prisoners were also reformed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Commissioner of Prisons Chandana Ekanayake said that many inmates who appeared for the high-level exams for 2021 have improved.",
        "He said that every year the examinations work with the department to create opportunities for deserving inmates to pursue higher education and for that, 3 inmates detained in Colombo Magazine Jail failed the examination this time.",
        "He said that a 38-year-old prisoner was a former member of the LTTE and had obtained \"c\" grades in Geography and Hindu Civilization and \"S\" grades in Tamil language.",
        "Similarly, a 46-year-old prisoner detained in the Welikada jail has obtained S Siddhis in Sinhala, Buddhism and Political Science."
      ],
